Have you visited the weird house just
below here? There's a game called
Tiger! Tiger! just by the entrance.

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I tried playing it once, just to see
what it was like, but it was scarily
addictive. I had fun for hours!

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0003
rows.name:
My high score right now is
18,310 points!

rows.label: tlk41100124_04_msg0004
rows.name:
My dream was to become a botanical
scientist, but maybe I should become a
pro Tiger! Tiger! player instead...
